{"tid":2029470,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"外交部：香港事務純屬中國內政　外國無權干預","createTime":"2020-05-22T08:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T11:41:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"42b224760a5d701414778751b6bee026550a46b6","tid":2029470,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:53:34.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，若果中國因為香港去年反修例示威引發的激烈衝突，對香港實施國家安全法，美國會有強烈回應。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅重申，中方堅定不移維護國家主權、安全、發展利益；對貫徹「一國兩制」方針，及反對任何外部勢力干涉香港事務的決心，亦是堅定不移。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅強調，香港是中國的特區，香港特區維護國家安全立法的問題，純屬中國內政，任何外國無權干預，而放眼世界亦無任何國家，允許自己的領土上，有人從事分裂等危害國家安全的活動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527742-20200522.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527742-20200522.htm&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSi2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=d1c3dd17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527742-20200522.htm&h=061d296a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527742-20200522.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a53a55747e0980b4680c5ec0635e18c29a0ccd34","tid":2029470,"uid":125502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"ecb58c499dda9c9af63de7656dc2f90569ae6af1","tid":2029470,"uid":14494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:09:40.000Z","msg":"你個國安法明郁外國人外資喎"},{"pid":"9e88bc98022af921cbd624da018ed70ed97ab6a